title: Street Fighter V Leaked Video Confirms Rashid Arab Character
text: Street Fighter V has just received a brand new character in the form of Arab fighter Rashid. The confirmation isn't official just yet but a full-fledged gameplay trailer has leaked online, alongside a reveal from Dubai. Street Fighter V promises to deliver the next evolution in the long running fighting series made by Japanese company Capcom.
